<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
        <p>Hi <%= it.username %>,</p>
        <p>We received a request to change the password for your account. If you made this request, please click the link below to reset your password:</p>
        <p>
            <a href="<%= it.url %>">Reset Password</a>
        </p>
        <p>For security purposes, this link will expire in 15 hours. If you did not request a password change, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>Your Company Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>